<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM1.5">
<l>vāṉiṭai vāḻumav vāṉavarkku maṟaiyavar vēḷviyil vakuttavavi</l>
<l>kāṉiṭait tirivatōr naripukuntu kaṭappatu mōppatuñ ceyvatoppa</l>
<l>vūṉiṭai yāḻicaṅkut tamarkkeṉ ṟuṉṉit teḻuntaveṉ ṟaṭamulaikaḷ</l>
<l>māṉiṭa varkkeṉṟu pēccuppaṭil vāḻakil lēṉkaṇṭāy maṉmataṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Similar to the deeds of a forest-roaming jackal</l>
<l>that enters [the sacrificial hall], steps over, and sniffs</l>
<l rend="indent">the offerings that the Brahmins distribute during the sacrifice</l>
<l rend="indent">for the beautiful, sky-dwelling celestials,</l>
<l>if my large breasts—which rose and grew for the sake of</l>
<l rend="indent">the Superior [Lord] with a discus [and] a conch on [His] body,</l>
<l>are spoken of as meant for humans, I shall not be able to live. See, O Manmatha!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
